Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:00:59.95,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Far off into the expanse of yellow sand ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:03.15,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Comes great longing for a parted person ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.74,0:01:06.15,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Moonlight like water, clouds like smoke ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:09.43,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ When did it once shine down ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:12.27,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Afraid of mortal greed abiding ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:15.47,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Can’t help answer your thousand words with ten thousand of mine ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:18.83,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Back then a farewell, now meeting again ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:21.99,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Lingering quietly grows from the fingertips ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:27.23,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Even if your ears, nose, brows, eyes can’t be forgotten ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:34.03,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Yet still wait for the two of us to have debts never more ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.18,0:01:35.39,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Gathering orchids on an empty mountain ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:36.91,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Searching for butterflies over the sea ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:39.83,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Too much love and hate ultimately precludes fulfillment ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.34,0:01:41.55,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Thrilling experiences rush by ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:43.31,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Endlessly distant heaven and earth ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:46.19,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Drooping eyes are all in the past ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:47.71,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Lonely when you go ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.86,0:01:49.11,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Yet dreams are indistinct when you return ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:52.15,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Perhaps this love may not be as wished ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:53.71,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Countless feelings overwhelm ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:55.63,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Heart is shaken while still young ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.02,0:01:58.63,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Asking who can, by whom, ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:01:59.79,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ be exempt ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:07.02,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fade(640,640)}Battle Through The Heavens - Season 3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:03:02.34,NEXT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(600,400)\pos(1792,530)}Recap
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I die,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make you merge with the Flame Mantra!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Teacher’s only hope for resurrection!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Xiao Yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve successfully proven that this Flame Mantra
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,really can swallow Heavenly Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Its potential
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is indeed limitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And your potential
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,is also limitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I really did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,let’s go find Hai Bodong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This stinky brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:08.70,Episode,,0,0,0,,{\fade(640,640)\pos(977,722)}Episode 9
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:18.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fade(460,360)\pos(1730,535)}Hai Bodong
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:13.66,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fade(460,360)\pos(575,208)}Mo Ran
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what secrets does this map possess?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Little fellow,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you’ve finally returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve really made me wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you brought back..?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Sand Datura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing was far too difficult to look for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Within the Snake People Shrine,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only lucky to find one just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have really troubled you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Hai,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve already brought back the goods for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That map fragment,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldn’t you give it to me first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What we agreed upon back then
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,was that after you refine and give me the seal breaking pill,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I would give you the map fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:03:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can be considered to owe you a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that Old Hai,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,after receiving the pill,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,will keep your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,although I’m good-tempered,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,what I hate most is being played for a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is underneath the desert,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,a secret space I formed using an ice seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how great the disturbance inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the outer world won’t know a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty sturdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Little fellow,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the recipe and ingredients needed to refine the Breaking Adversity Pill
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,are all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Hai,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,things like refining medicinal pills
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,always have a chance of failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Refining a Tier 6 pill,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,although I have some confidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t make any guarantees.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.36,0:04:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If refinement fails in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,this liability...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Alchemists should not be liable,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand this principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,During refinement,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I require absolute quiet;
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot allow anyone to disturb me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That includes you yourself, Old Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I will stand guard outside the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There will definitely not be anyone who would dare barge inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I leave everything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing’s wrong with this place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,En.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I checked;
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that fellow hasn’t set up any tricks here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Breaking Adversity Pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tier 6 pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It has the unique effect of breaking most kinds of seals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Really quite a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,time to get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you would make these old bones of mine do hard labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d like to do things myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but with what little alchemy ability I have,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to refine a Tier 6 medicinal pill
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is just delusional.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,While Teacher is refining the pill later,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you should diligently observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be of great benefit to your improvement in alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood, Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive cauldron.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A medicinal cauldron
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is the most important thing an alchemist possesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A good cauldron
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,can greatly increase the success rate of pill refinement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This cauldron of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is known as
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,“Black Demon.”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Black Demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure is domineering.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,look carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafting medicinal fragrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the pill is about to form!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A special ice body coagulated by the Bone Chilling Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Once mixed into the pill and swallowed by someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,it will slip into their body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, it will not have the slightest unusual activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,if activated by my Heavenly Flame,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1072)}these ice bodies will swiftly transform into extremely destructive Bone Chilling Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You should never let down your guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is only a self-defense measure of alchemists.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Old people really are more shrewd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Pill, arise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a Tier 6 medicinal pill’s power?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,it’s like this pill developed a spirit of its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The product doesn’t look bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Stinky brat,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,there’s actually some mystical force.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is probably the element that breaks the seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it have failed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I was reckless;
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,although I unable to fully see through that fellow’s strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,he is too young, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Little fellow,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,did it succeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just got lucky,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.28,0:09:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,somehow managed to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Breaking Adversity Pill?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Little fellow really does hide his abilities deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Hai,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve already refined the pill for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the map fragment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Little fellow,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,after I confirm that this pill is the Breaking Adversity Pill,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I will use both hands to offer the map fragment to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me remind you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,if you use the pill,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but due to the recipe you provided
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the seal still isn’t broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,would you place the blame on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I traveled thousands of miles in the desert,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,taking the risk of getting killed by Queen Medusa
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to help you find Sand Datura,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and even expended all effort to refine a medicinal pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All this you’ve ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Hai,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve done so much
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.68,0:10:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in exchange for nothing but a map fragment
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and a Fight Emperor’s verbal promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,did I lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,or did I gain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Stinky brat,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you’ve gotten better and better at talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,when dealing with this kind of person,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to strike first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Little fellow,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as this Breaking Adversity Pill can produce the smallest effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:10:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t go back on my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as you like then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me caution Old Hai,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the last time I’m capitulating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Many thanks for your understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now take the Breaking Adversity Pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,this old fellow won’t go back on us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as he takes the Breaking Adversity Pill,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,he won’t be able to pose a threat to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,he swallowed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The seal
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is about to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This damned seal has finally disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I am now a Fight Emperor once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Hai,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,this stance of yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you’re not going to kill the donkey after it drove the mill, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This kid, being able to refine a Tier 6 pill at such a young age.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Such geniuses you can only befriend;
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot become enemies with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Little brother Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,how could I forget the help you provided me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of ungrateful action,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the old me will not do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I sincerely apologize,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,just then was because I suddenly recovered my strength
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and found it difficult to control my Dou Qi for a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve startled you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I originally also wanted to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the true strength of Ice Emperor, who once dominated the Jia Ma Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Little brother Xiao Yan is joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the agreement,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,this map fragment is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There is tremendous spiritual energy within;
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,it is indeed that map fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I express many thanks to Old Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Little brother Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.48,0:13:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you seem to be very interested in the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,this should only be one of many map fragments.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you can tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that after gathering the fragments,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,what will be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.16,0:13:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I only encountered this kind of map fragment at an auction once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what they are hiding,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I am also unsure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,he’s anticipating all of my attack patterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Better decide this quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Triple Lightning
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Arc Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where’d he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Brother is no match for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Trash is trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This pitiful strength
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,yet trying to be my opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Company Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one seeking death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me give you brothers a ride
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m taking it today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Company Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve come late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You all carefully tend to your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,let me handle him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is called Mo Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:17:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A One-star Fight Grandmaster Luo Bu found from who knows where.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,His Qi Method is of the Earth affinity
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,which is well suited to drawn out fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,One-star Fight Grandmaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you don’t need to intervene this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to take this man’s life myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,En.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d advise not setting yourself on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just this Desert Metal Mercenary Company
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,isn’t anywhere close to being our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,kneel on the ground and beg for mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I might even forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough with the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all you’ve got?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually dare to bluff in front of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This power is too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:17:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,now you know where meddling gets you, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Obediently leave your life behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Yan, he—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,his opponent is a Fight Grandmaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Yan without that strange black ruler
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is actually his strongest state.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and this Desert Metal Mercenary Company bunch of fools,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I will have all of you disappear today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,After completing the Clan Head’s orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can leave this godforsaken place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yan City’s Mo Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You brat,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you actually know of the Mo Clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Dou Qi armor that Fight Grandmasters can agglomerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately it hasn’t been long since I entered Fight Grandmaster;
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise Dou Qi armor could cover my entire body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,your attack power
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot possibly break it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Dou Qi armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t believe
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that your turtle shell can’t be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Little shit,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,getting a taste of Dou Qi armor
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and dying in my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn’t be bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Relying on yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,believing in your own strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the conviction held by strong practitioners.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The current you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is on the way to becoming a strong practitioner.
